{
  "stem": "16163.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know which one it was, but I know Dr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Edelstain went to Auschwitz with a family transport before I did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "With the family, and that was a-- I think [? succor ?] was name also.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He [? was ?] something in the, you know, in a Judenrat or whatever they called it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were appointed from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really have no idea how they did it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course it was a good position, because you had your own rooms, and you had your-- a different type of a ghetto life then we had.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was an easier life, but they went earlier than us to Auschwitz and none of them came back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were killed-- first ones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They called [INAUDIBLE] they were called the [GERMAN], prominent to the other people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were transports going in 1943 and 1944, and 1944 mainly, to Auschwitz with only prominent people on there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it wasn't only from the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were other prominents also, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had a Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was called a ghetto [? worker, ?] and they were just men and women.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A few of them were women, I believe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know if there were women.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I really-- I really don't-- I think there were few women in the ghetto [? worker ?] too, and the men.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they were just regular Jewish citizens who came from all over like we did, and then were appointed to work there as ghetto [? worker. ?]",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That also was considered a better position, but most of them didn't make it anyway, so--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Their function was that-- we had, for instance, a curfew at night, a certain time every-- the whole ghetto had to be inside.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
